Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.16,0:27:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinami Haruka - Murasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.32,0:27:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Muro Cujoši - Merebu
